{
  "stem": "10353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on a Sunday, the vice-- the regent, Horty-- H-O-R-T-Y-- made an announcement that the Hungarians are suing for peace, or to surrender.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, by that time, of course, they were occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in no time, the Germans swooped down all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They arrested the regent and everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Arrow Cross people took over the government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all hell broke loose at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because on Monday morning, I ventured out because my commanding officer gave me a false document saying-- which was in the form of a book, which every military personnel had to have.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It-- with a picture on it, with everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It said that I'm Greek Catholic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I ventured out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ventured out with-- from our compound, and I went to see my boss for whom I worked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a [INAUDIBLE], a daughter, an only daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I tried to sort of smuggle out the daughter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His daughter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to their apartment and thought that I can take her to a safe place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I had to-- I had to make my way in from the compound into the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I was going in, there were corpses already lying on the streets, covered with newspapers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These Arrow Cross people were going around killing Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the minute the regent made that announcement by the Hungarians, the Jewish people ventured out of the Jewish-designated houses, which were formed into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from then on, there was open, blatant physical [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] persecution and killings going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They rounded up-- wherever they could find a Jew, they rounded them up.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
